(thirdQuint)18F-FES PET/CT in Imaging Patients With Desmoid Tumors.

 PRIMARY OBJECTIVES: I.

 Establish the avidity of desmoid tumors on 18F-FES PET/CT imaging.

 II.

 Correlate 18F-FES PET avidity with degree of estrogen receptor (ER) expression by immunohistochemistry (IHC).

 OUTLINE: Patients undergo 18F-FES PET/CT imaging over 30 minutes.

 After completion of study, patients are followed up for 30 days.

